## Snippet Tool Usage

### Full File
```
mcp_xcf_snippet(filePath="file.swift", entireFile=true)
```

### Line Range
```
mcp_xcf_snippet(filePath="file.swift", startLine=10, endLine=20)
```

### Human Command
```
mcp_xcf_snippet filePath="file.swift" entireFile=true     // Entire file
mcp_xcf_snippet filePath="file.swift" startLine=10 endLine=20     // Line range
```

## Analyzer Tool Usage

### Full File Analysis
```
mcp_xcf_analyzer(filePath="file.swift", entireFile=true)
```

### Line Range Analysis
```
mcp_xcf_analyzer(filePath="file.swift", startLine=10, endLine=20)
```

### Human Command
```
mcp_xcf_analyzer filePath="file.swift" entireFile=true           // Entire file
mcp_xcf_xcf action="lz file.swift"                               // Shorthand (entire file)
mcp_xcf_analyzer filePath="file.swift" startLine=10 endLine=20   // Line range
```

## Common Workflows

### Basic Project Workflow
```
use xcf
grant
show
open 1
build
run
```

### Code Analysis Workflow
```
mcp_xcf_xcf action="use xcf"
mcp_xcf_xcf action="current"
mcp_xcf_snippet filePath="Main.swift" entireFile=true
mcp_xcf_analyzer filePath="Main.swift" entireFile=true
```
